Package: cutoffvalue
Title: Cutoff Value Determination & Graph
Version: 2.1.0
Year: 2025
Authors@R: 
    person("Lea", "Medeiros", "R", "lmedeiros@uidaho.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6944-4935"))
URL: <https://github.com/lea-medeiros/cutoffvalue>, <https://lea-medeiros.github.io/cutoffvalue/>
Description: This is a simple R package that implements an updated version of the method first developed and used in Medeiros et al. (2018). It can be used to determine an objective cutoff value between a significantly bimodal distribution of log-transformed data and plot a representative graph of the results.
